entities.c: STANCE-Rance: Seeks his counsel before presenting decisions to Selenay—treating him as collaborative partner rather than subordinate despite rank difference. Comfortable visiting his isolated cottage alone at dawn. Shifted from vulnerable confusion to decisive action overnight regarding shared-memory situation. Uses formal Court cadence when discussing matters of weight.
